OOC: Well rAuq left, so Pacifix didnt do anything for a while as well.

IC: It dawned on Pacifix. "You were a former Maximal. Come with me and
give me a hand in that area." Pacifix invited Torca, hoping for a chance
to get to learn about the Maximals. The transport part of his vehicle
mode opened up. "Slag you might as well come for backup. The rest of
you, make Gesper feel at home."
